stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> Queued
    Queued --> Dispatch : worker free

    state Fork <<fork>>
    Dispatch --> Fork

    state Shard {
        [*] --> Mapping
        Mapping --> Mapped : emit pairs
        Mapped --> [*]
    }

    Fork --> Shard
    Fork --> Reduce : stream
    Reduce : Reduce partials

    state Join <<join>>
    Shard --> Join
    Reduce --> Join

    Join --> Aggregate : combine
    Aggregate --> Decision
    state Decision <<choice>>
    Decision --> Done : success
    Decision --> Retry : transient error
    Retry --> Dispatch : backoff
    Done --> [*]

    note right of Join : Barrier — waits for\nall shards + reduce
    classDef ok fill:#238636,stroke:#ffffff,color:#ffffff
    class Done ok
